###
# Test Users API

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users

### Get users with pagination and search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users?search=&page=1&pageSize=5

### Get total count of users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/count

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "username": "alice123",
  "image": "https://example.com/alice.jpg",
  "role": "user",
  "following": [],
  "followers": [],
  "bio": "Hello, I'm Alice!"
}

### Update a user
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Updated bio!"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/5

### ============================================================
### Follow / Unfollow / Followers
### ============================================================

### Follow a user — Jett (4) follows Sova (3)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/3/follow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "followerId": 5
}

### Unfollow a user — Jett (4) unfollows Sova (3)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/3/follow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "followerId": 5
}

### Remove a follower — Sova (3) removes Jett (5) from their followers
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/3/followers/5

### Get all users that user 4 (Jett) is following
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/5/following

### Get all followers of user 1 (Clove)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1/followers


###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "clove@valorant.protocol.com"
}
